Package: CQLConnect
Type: Package
Title: CQLConnect - Dispatch cql to query a Cassandra database via scala
Version: 2.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Akhil", "Nair", email = "akhil.nair@amey.co.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Maintainer: Akhil Nair <akhil.nair@amey.co.uk>
Description: This is not a generic package currently - It queries a single row
    from a specific data model as this is the only functionality I required. A 
    more generic package requires introspection to infer model classes and a way
    to send the scala equivalent of dataframes back to R 
